thread.title: 2015 leaderboards

author: The Telegraph
title: 2015 leaderboards
text: The latest leaderboards from the Telegraph BMW Junior Golf Championship 2015 hosted by Quinta do Lago will be posted here throughout the year and will be updated on a weekly basis. These are correct at time of publication. If you have any queries regarding any of the leaderboards please call the championship hotline on 0344 693 1885. Scores will only be placed on the leaderboard when the organiser of the qualifier has sent back the results and these have been verified July 24, 2015 Open competitions Boys gross leaderboard Girls gross leaderboard Boys net leaderboard Girls net leaderboard July 27, 2015 Girls net leaderboard
